COMMAND : 

<picture>
  <source srcset="<PATHTOIMAGEFORSMALDISPLAY>" media="(max-width: <RESOLUTION>px)">
  <img src="<PATHTOIMAGEFORBIGDISPLAY>" style="width:auto;">
</picture>

EXAMPLE : 

<picture>
  <source srcset="background-images-for-smal-displays.jpg" media="(max-width: 600px)">
  <img src="background-images-for-big-displays.jpg" alt="Flowers" style="width:auto;">
</picture>

EXPLANATION :

<PATHTOIMAGEFORSMALDISPLAY>   This image will be show if the display is smaler than the defined RESOLUTION
<PATHTOIMAGEFORBIGDISPLAY>    This image will be show if the display is bigger than the defined RESOLUTION
<RESOLUTION>                  This will define the size when the image should change depending on the display size
